track_notes: Route represents combined activation of Hazeltop and nearby Fork Mtn.
track_title: W4V/SH-004 Hazeltop Mtn and W4V/SH-003 Fork Mtn

track_notes:
This time of year, the seasonal WMA gate at (38.47078, -78.38284) for the Fork Mtn fire road should be open, and you can drive up to the second gate at (38.46290, -78.40054).

Theres just enough shoulder at the second gate to park without blocking access for comm site personnel. The walk from here to the summit is 2.7 mi each way.

The roads were doable in my SUV. 4WD advisable due to large mud holes on the Rapidan fire road. Surface conditions might have changed for better or worse due to recent firefighter access to the Quaker Run fire.
track_title: Fork Mtn Access from Rapidan WMA

track_notes: This is the track for when the seasonal WMA gate at (38.47078, -78.38284) for the Fork Mtn fire road should is closed.
track_title: Fork Mtn Access from Rapidan River
